41:15.453 --> 41:19.698
Lord, I thank You for Your mercies, for Your goodness, for Your grace in our lives,

41:19.810 --> 41:22.036
We thank you for everything you have done for us.

41:22.116 --> 41:26.749
You went to the cross, you died for us, and you rose again for us, and you're coming back for us.

41:27.571 --> 41:33.106
Thank you for this in Christ and on all God's people said, Amen.

